  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "E-commerce specialist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are seeking a driven and detail-oriented E-commerce Specialist to manage and grow Midea’s online sales channels in Singapore. You will lead daily e-commerce operations, execute and optimize campaigns, analyze performance data, and collaborate closely with internal teams and external platform partners to drive sales growth and enhance brand presence.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage and operate Midea’s e-commerce platforms including Shopee, Lazada, TikTok Shop, and Brand.com to maximize sales and customer engagement</li><li>Plan, execute, and optimize online campaigns, promotions, and key sales events such as 9.9, 11.11, and 12.12 to drive measurable sales growth</li><li>Monitor daily sales performance, website traffic, conversion rates, and campaign effectiveness to identify opportunities for improvement</li><li>Coordinate cross-functionally with marketing, product, logistics, and customer service teams to ensure seamless e-commerce operations</li><li>Maintain accurate and up-to-date product listings, pricing, promotions, and stock availability to support sales objectives</li><li>Collaborate with platform account managers to leverage campaign mechanics, visibility tools, and performance enhancement strategies</li><li>Analyze sales data and prepare regular performance reports with actionable insights to inform strategic decisions</li><li>Ensure consistent brand representation across all e-commerce touchpoints to strengthen brand identity</li><li>Track competitors’ pricing, promotions, and market trends to maintain competitive positioning</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Demonstrated hands-on experience in e-commerce operations with a minimum of 1–3 years, preferably in consumer electronics</li><li>Proficiency in using Excel and platform dashboards for data analysis to monitor and improve e-commerce performance</li><li>Strong communication and coordination skills to effectively collaborate with cross-functional teams</li><li>Proficient in written and spoken English to support clear communication within the team and with partners</li><li>Ability to manage multiple campaigns simultaneously in a fast-paced environment while meeting tight deadlines</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Bachelor’s Degree in E-commerce, Business, Marketing, or related field</li><li>Familiarity with major e-commerce platforms in Singapore such as Shopee, Lazada, and TikTok Shop</li><li>Knowledge of Mandarin to facilitate liaison with regional teams</li></ul>",
